data.text:
You must pick up your passport in person at this location. It will be ready by the end of the next business day.

You must provide proof of travel to receive urgent service.

There is an extra fee for urgent pick-up ($110).

After we process your application, weâll mail your passport to you.

The service standard (opens in a new tab) for processing your application at this location is 20 business days.

Service standards do not include mail time. Mail time is usually 5 business days but can vary across the country.

After we process your application, weâll mail your passport to you.

The service standard (opens in a new tab) for processing your application at this location is 10 business days.

Service standards do not include mail time. Mail time is usually 5 business days but can vary across the country.

Proof you need the passport can be

an airline, bus or train ticket

If travelling by car, a written statement explaining why you need to travel

a travel itinerary showing proof of payment

proof of illness or death in the family requiring you to travel

a written statement from you or a third party explaining why you need the passport

For example, for legal, banking or residency requirements

If we can’t deliver the passport in time to you or your child, we aren’t liable for any losses.

We recommend that you don’t finalize any travel plans until you get your passport.
